[00:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hiko\'s XRVP is a professional platform built around an integrated virtual production workflow, placing real subjects inside virtual environments to reimagine how visual content is made from film and television to commercials'

[00:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and broadcast. Unlike traditional onloation shoots or green screen workflows, HEO\'s XRVP removes the constraints of time and'

[00:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'place. Real-time rendered 3D environments replace physical set construction, offering greater creative flexibility while keeping production within a controlled studio environment, reducing the costs and logistical risks'

[00:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'of mobilizing a crew. Directors and performers see a near final composite as it is being shot, enabling precise creative decisions on set rather than in post-prouction.'

[01:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Before cameras roll, the entire creative team works within the same provisualized environment, blocking shots, refining lighting, composition, and movement in'

[01:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'advance. Technical risks are identified and resolved at the pre-production stage, significantly reducing uncertainty in post and giving the team full confidence in the creative outcome.'

[01:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Built on a media server architecture developed for live performance, Kiko\'s XRVP brings rapid deployment to the film'

[01:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'set through color calibration, lens calibration, spatial positioning, and latency calibration. The system is ready to shoot in minutes. By eliminating lengthy technical setup, the team\'s time'

[01:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and energy stay focused on the creative work that matters. Heat. Heat. N.'
